registrable.singleobjective

Class PipeOptimizingRegister

  • java.lang.Object
    • registrable.singleobjective.PipeOptimizingRegister
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Registrable<Experiment<?>>, SingleObjectiveRegistrable

    public final class PipeOptimizingRegister
extends Object
implements SingleObjectiveRegistrable
    Class that describe the problem to be showned in menu of problem in the GUI.

    The sistem read this class using reflection to get the annotation and create a GUI to configure the experiment and inject the value to injectable method.

        numberWithoutImprovement - the number without improvement in the result
